---
// Nenhuma lógica do servidor necessária
---

<section id="quem-sou" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-end justify-center overflow-hidden pt-24 lg:pt-24">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div 
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 bottom-0 z-0 bg-cover bg-center animate-zoom-in"
    style="background-image: url('/images/ft_arruda01.jpg'); background-attachment: fixed;"
  >
    <!-- Overlay escuro para melhor legibilidade -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Conteúdo -->
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
      <!-- Título Principal -->
      <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Olá, bem vindo à <span class="text-black" style="color: #0a504c;">Serra Gaúcha</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-100">
          Sou Filippi Arruda, da TourLive na Serra Gaúcha. Meu propósito é conduzir você com segurança, hospitalidade e amor pela história local — para que cada passeio se torne uma memória viva.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Botões de Ação -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
        <a 
          href="#contato" 
          class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 scroll-smooth shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Entre em contato</span>
        </a>
        
        <a 
          href="#passeios" 
          class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 scroll-smooth shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Veja os passeios</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Estatísticas -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-2">500+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-200">Clientes Satisfeitos</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-2">5</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-200">Anos de Experiência</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-2">4.9</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-200">Avaliação Média</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Seta para baixo -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10">
    <a href="#passeios" class="text-white hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors animate-bounce">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes zoom-in {
    0% {
      transform: scale(1.2);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
  
  .animate-zoom-in {
    animation: zoom-in 2s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>